text: Sokol Bishanaku (born 2 June 1971), is a former Albanian weightlifter who competed at the 1992 Summer Olympic Games .Sports-Reference Profile He is now a national coach. ==References== Category:Weightlifters at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic weightlifters of Albania Category:Living people Category:1971 births Category:Albanian male weightlifters
